snippet.title: Carlos Sainz gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Carlos Sainz, Dos PC game produced by Zigurat in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/carlos-sainz/6581/
Carlos Sainz is a famous Spanish game, racing, arcade style. It is a racing game quite good, with many circuits.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
